@node Main "A2Zee - Documentation"

                                A2Zee 1.06

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  @{" A2Zee " link play} is a game where you try to put a row of letters in an
alphabetical order in the least amount of moves possible.

  You can choose to play with as few as 8 letters up to all the
letters of the alphabet.

  Have fun!

